데카르트 좌표계로 간주하는 매개변수 공간 또는 데카르트 좌표계 실공간에 대한 gradient 이다. 1. Scalar gradient $$ 
abla\varphi = rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial\vec{u}} = rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial u_i}\hat{u}_i = rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial u_1}\hat{u}_1+ rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial u_2}\hat{u}_+ rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial u_3}\hat{u}_3 $$ 2. Vector Gradient $$ 
abla\vec{f} = rac{\partial \vec{f}}{\partial\vec{u}} = rac{\partial f_j}{\partial u_i}\hat{u}_i\hat{u}_j $$전개하면, 다음과 같으며, 2차 텐서임을 알 수 있다. $$  egin{align} 
abla\vec{f} = &  rac{\partial f_1}{\partial u_1}\hat{u}_1\hat{u}_1 +  rac{\partial f_1}{\partial u_2}\hat{u}_2\hat{u}_1 +  rac{\partial f_1}{\partial u_3}\hat{u}_3\hat{u}_1 \ &  rac{\partial f_2}{\partial u_1}\hat{u}_1\hat{u}_2 +  rac{\partial f_2}{\partial u_2}\hat{u}_2\hat{u}_2 +  rac{\partial f_2}{\partial u_3}\hat{u}_3\hat{u}_2 \ &  rac{\partial f_3}{\partial u_1}\hat{u}_1\hat{u}_3 +  rac{\partial f_3}{\partial u_2}\hat{u}_2\hat{u}_3 +  rac{\partial f_3}{\partial u_3}\hat{u}_3\hat{u}_3 \end{align} $$ 3. Conjugate vector gradient $$ \vec{f}
abla = rac{\partial f_i}{\partial u_j}\hat{u}_i\hat{u}_j $$$$ [
abla\vec{f}]^{T} =\vec{f}
abla $$ 4. Vector gradient & Kronecker delta $$ 
abla\vec{u} = rac{\partial \vec{u}}{\partial \vec{u}} = rac{\partial u_i}{\partial u_j}\hat{u}_i\hat{u}_j =[\delta_{ij}] = ar{ ar{I}} $$ 5. High tensor gradient 2차 텐서에서,
